data.title: Horizon High School
data.meta_description: Horizon High School is the home of the Huskies, one of the best K-12 High Schools in the valley
data.text:
There is a lot more to PVSchools than just academics! Start your journey today and find out what it's like in Paradise!

Thank you for being part of our community, for choosing PVSchools, and for all you do to support student success. Let's make this year the best one yet!
